import { CHANGEID, CHANGEKEYWORD } from "./constant"

const initState = ""

export default function Reducer(preState = initState, action) {
    const { type, data } = action
    let result = []
    switch (type) {
        case CHANGEKEYWORD:
            result[0] = data
            return data
        case CHANGEID:
            result[1] = data
            return data
        default:
            return result
    }
}
